I loved this film. No car chases, explosions or violence, just a guy working his way through life while staying true to his family roots and culture. What a blessing to be able to share this with young people to show them the value in staying connected with family and tradition. Thanks for the glimpse into your life Cory.

A real time, real life, entrepreneurial, adventure of living off the land.  It is not easy living being traditional in modern times but Cory Mann shows us how to go with the flow.  You can never have enough sockeye!
